longBusinessSummary: Industrial Tech Acquisitions II, Inc. does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. The company intends to focus its search on targets operating in the technology-focused areas, including software, mobile and IoT applications, digital and energy transformation, cloud, and cyber communications, as well as high bandwidth services, including LTE, remote sensing, and 5G communications. Industrial Tech Acquisitions II, Inc. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Houston, Texas.
